        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "We laugh now! Victoria did not laugh then.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000007_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000007_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "On the instant, every girl was offered some kind of situation, which she voluntarily and almost immediately exchanged for matrimony.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
