    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "He stood for the rights of the poorest miner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "In private life he was fond of music, art, and literature; but in public life he was autocratic as a czar and sternly righteous as a prophet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "He was a vigilance committee in himself through sheer force of personality.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "From hating and fearing him, the camp came almost to worship him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "Many are the stories of his circuits.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "You deserve to be hanged.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "Had the jury performed their duty, I might have the painful satisfaction of condemning you to death.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "You, gentlemen of the jury, permit me to say that it would give me great pleasure to sentence you to be hanged each and every one of you, for bringing in a murderer guilty only of manslaughter.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
