        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "Mr Alexander, one of the Overlanders of 'sixty two, tells how 'Begbie's decisions may not have been good law, but they were first-class justice.' His 'doctrine was that if a man were killed, some one had to be hanged for it; and the effect was salutary.' A man had been sandbagged in a Victoria saloon and thrown out to die.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "His companion in the saloon was arrested and tried.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "The circumstantial evidence was strong, and the judge so charged the jury.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-9026_282385_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/9026/282385/9026_282385_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-9026",
        "content": "But the jury acquitted the prisoner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
